<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Science_fiction&amp;action=edit&amp;section=31" title="Edit section: Asia">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Asia</span></h3>
<div class="rellink noprint relarticle mainarticle">Main article: <a href="/wiki/Science_fiction_of_Bangladesh" title="Science fiction of Bangladesh" class="mw-redirect">Science fiction of Bangladesh</a></div>
